vallibrary.measures
Class FMIndex

java.lang.Object
  vallibrary.measures.Measure
      vallibrary.measures.FMIndex

public class FMIndex
extends Measure

The FMIndex class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Fowlkes and Mallows Index. This class takes in input a Data Matrix and an Input_Measure object. Measure values are returned in a Measure_Vector object with values ranging between 0 and 1.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Raffaele Giancarlo, Davide Scaturro, Filippo Utro
